Masha Allah Bada Masjid Hai, Aur Bagepalli Ka MARKAZ Ka Hai Dawat Ke Kaam Ka, Sub'hanallaah

Allah Ta'ala ne tamaam insaanon ki duniya ki zindagi aur Aakhirat yaani marne ke baad ki zindagi ki kaamyabi sirf "Deen" mein rakhi hai, Allah Ta'ala ke hukmon ko pura karne aur Aap  ki bataaye huwe tareeqon ke mutaabiq chalne ka naam "Deen" hai. Lihaaza har musalmaan ke liye zaroori hai ke woh apni zindagi ke har shobe mein Allah Ta'ala ka hukm aur Hazrat Muhammad  ka tareeqa maaloom kar ke us par amal kare aur us ko logon tak pohnchaane ki fikr kare. featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Assalamu Alaikum Warahmatullahi Wa Barakatuhu,

Masha Allah Bada Masjid Hai, Aur Bagepalli Ka Markaz Hai Dawat Ke Kaam Ka, Sub'hanallaah

Allah Ta'ala has kept the entire life of human beings in this world and the hereafter i.e. the success of life after death only in "Deen", the name of fulfilling the orders of Allah Ta'ala and following the directions shown by you (peace be upon him). "Deen" is. Therefore, it is important for every Muslim to know the rule of Allah Ta'ala and the order of Hazrat Muhammad (PBUH) in every aspect of his life, follow it and think of spreading it to the people. Therefore, it is very important that a Muslim spend some time with his worldly occupations to acquire at least as much knowledge as is obligatory on him and try to acquire more and more knowledge and apply it.

I pray to Allah Ta'ala that those who build a mosque and pray for it, may Allah bless them and pray for them.. (Ameen) (Suma Ameen)
